    "text": [
        "Mr Brian",
        "I am writing to you in order to ask permission for a time off.\u2028 I need these days off as my mother is visiting me on 17th July after a long time from abroad. We need some alone time together to catch up and without a vacation it is not possible. Furthermore, as she never been in the USA, I want to show her some places.",
        "As you know, all my yearly leaves are still due, I would like to take two weeks vacation. In the first week, i want to show her some of the scenic places around Rochester and the second week would be reserved for attending marriage ceremony of my cousin who resides in Chicago.",
        "I had already organized my works and handed it over to Prashanth. He is willing to take care of my responsibilities for those following weeks and i will be in regular contact with him. In case of emergency, any one can reach out to me through my personal phone number and time to time i will check my emails.\u2028\u2028I hope there will be no issue while i am gone.",
        "Please let me know if you have any suggestions for me regarding this leave.",
        "Best regards",
        "Ashik Sarwar"
